## Design Panel Sections (Right Panel)

Full section list in render order:

0. **Content** *(Text/Heading + any container with Text/Heading child)* ŌĆö Textarea to edit `node.text` directly. Shown before Position & Size.
1. **Position & Size** ŌĆö X/Y (read-only DOM metrics), W/H (inline `style.width/height` + `minWidth/minHeight: 0`)
2. **Dimensions** ŌĆö W mode: Hug (`w-fit`) / Fill (`w-full`) / Fixed (removes fit/full). H mode: same with `h-*`. Also: Min W / Max W / Min H / Max H (inline `style.minWidth/maxWidth/minHeight/maxHeight`).
3. **Self Alignment** ŌĆö How this node aligns inside its parent flex container: `self-auto/start/center/end/stretch/baseline`
4. **Transform** ŌĆö Rotation (inline `style.transform = rotate(Ndeg)`), Flip H (`-scale-x-100`), Flip V (`-scale-y-100`)
5. **Alignment** *(containers only)* ŌĆö 9-cell grid (items-* + justify-*). Only shown for Box/VStack/HStack.
6. **Auto Layout** *(containers only)* ŌĆö Flex direction, wrap, gap (inline `style.gap`), space-between mode
7. **Padding** ŌĆö Exact pixel values via inline `style.paddingLeft/Right/Top/Bottom`. Combined H/V or individual toggle.
8. **Margin** ŌĆö Exact pixel values via inline `style.marginLeft/Right/Top/Bottom`. Combined H/V or individual toggle.
9. **Display & Interaction** ŌĆö Display type (`block/flex/grid/hidden`), Cursor (`cursor-pointer` etc.)
10. **Clip content** ŌĆö Toggle `overflow-hidden`
11. **Fill** ŌĆö Background color (inline `style.backgroundColor`, initialized from computed DOM color) + bg-opacity slider
12. **Stroke** ŌĆö Border color (inline `style.borderColor`, initialized from computed DOM color), border width, border style
13. **Effects** ŌĆö Drop shadow (`shadow-*` class)
14. **Typography** *(Text/Heading only)* ŌĆö Size, Weight, Leading, Tracking, Text alignment, Decoration, Transform, Text color (inline `style.color`, initialized from computed DOM color)
15. **Border Radius** ŌĆö 4-corner selects. All equal ŌåÆ single global token. Mixed ŌåÆ per-corner tokens.
16. **Opacity** ŌĆö Inline `style.opacity` (0ŌĆō1). Slider min=5.
17. **Selection colors** ŌĆö Hex swatches from className
18. **Layout Guide** ŌĆö Grid overlay toggle

