**Feature:** Dimensions section now includes 4 extra NumberInputs (Min W, Max W, Min H, Max H) that set `style.minWidth`, `style.maxWidth`, `style.minHeight`, `style.maxHeight` as pixel values. Setting to 0 clears the constraint.

**Rule:** Use inline style for these (not Tailwind `min-w-*` tokens) to allow exact pixel values.

