```

Renders: `LABEL | [toggle or ŲÆ Edit formula] [Ōēł]` ŌĆö all tightly grouped on the right (no flex-1 expansion).

**Rule:** Never use `FieldWithBinding` for toggle+bind rows. It has `flex: 1` which floats the Ōēł icon to the far right. Use `ToggleBind` instead.

