## ┬¦48 Form System ŌĆö E2E Test Patterns

E2E tests for forms live in `e2e/builder-form-validation.spec.ts`.

### Selecting form fields in Playwright

Use placeholder-based selectors for Gluestack inputs (they do not render a visible `<input type="email">` ŌĆö the type is set via `inputMode`):

```ts
// ŌØī BAD ŌĆö type-based selector unreliable with Gluestack
await page.locator('input[type="email"]').fill('test@test.com');

// Ō£ģ GOOD ŌĆö placeholder is always rendered
await page.locator('input[placeholder="Email"]').fill('test@test.com');

// Ō£ģ ALSO GOOD ŌĆö autocomplete attribute when placeholder is ambiguous
await page.locator('input[autocomplete="email"]').fill('test@test.com');
```

### Submitting forms

```ts
// Use text-based button selector (role-based can fail with Gluestack Button)
async function clickSubmit(page: Page, text = 'Sign In') {
  const btn = page.locator(`button:has-text("${text}"), [role="button"]:has-text("${text}")`).first();
  await btn.click();
}
```

### Testing debounced validation

```ts
// Type quickly ŌĆö error should NOT appear immediately
await page.locator('input[placeholder="Phone"]').fill('12');
await page.waitForTimeout(100); // less than debounce delay
await expect(page.locator('text=Invalid phone')).not.toBeVisible();

// Wait for debounce to fire
await page.waitForTimeout(600); // debounce is 500ms
await expect(page.locator('text=Invalid phone')).toBeVisible();
```

### Testing submit-trigger validation

```ts
// Clear field ŌĆö no error yet
await page.locator('input[placeholder="Email"]').fill('');
// Error should NOT appear before submit
await expect(page.locator('text=Required')).not.toBeVisible();
// Submit ŌĆö error should appear
await clickSubmit(page);
await expect(page.locator('text=Required')).toBeVisible();
```

### Validation clears on re-type

```ts
// After submit shows error, start typing ŌĆö error must clear
await page.locator('input[placeholder="Email"]').fill('a');
await expect(page.locator('text=Required')).not.toBeVisible();
```

