**Stability fix:** A `beforeEach` hook reloads the builder if the page URL has drifted (e.g. after a test failure that navigated away):
```ts
test.beforeEach(async () => {
  if (!sharedPage.url().includes('/dev/builder')) {
    await gotoBuilder(sharedPage);
  }
  await resetBuilder(sharedPage);
});
```
